ed="T" n="0813a02"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0813a02"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042324"><placeName>京兆</placeName><placeName>魏國寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A001194">惠立</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0813a03"/><persName key="A001194">釋惠立</persName>，本名<persName key="A001194">子立</persName>，<persName key="A002146">天皇</persName>改為<persName key="A001194">惠立</persName>，俗姓<name>趙</name><lb
ed="T" n="0813a04"/>氏，<placeName key="PL000000044976">天水</placeName>人也。遠祖因官<anchor xml:id="beg0813001"/>徙<anchor xml:id="end0813001"/>寓<placeName key="PL000000043171">新平</placeName>，故為<placeName key="PL000000043172">豳</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0813a05"/>人焉。爰祖及父，俱馳高譽。<persName key="A001194">立</persName>即<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName>起居舍人<lb
ed="T" n="0813a06"/>司隷從事<persName key="A011746">毅</persName>之第三子也。生而<anchor xml:id="beg0813sgsz1"/>岐嶷<anchor xml:id="end0813sgsz1"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1447"/>，有棄<lb
ed="T" n="0813a07"/>俗之志。年十五，<date from-iso="+0629-02-02" key="j19508301951213" to-iso="+0630-02-20"><name>貞觀</name>三年</date>出家，住<placeName key="PL000000043728"><placeName>豳州</placeName><placeName>昭仁<lb
ed="T" n="0813a08"/>寺</placeName></placeName>，此<ref type="place" target="#PL000000043728">寺</ref>即破<persName key="A011742">薛舉</persName>之戰場也<ptr target="#n2166"/>。<persName key="A001194">立</persName>識敏才俊，神<lb
ed="T" n="0813a09"/>清道邁，習<persName key="A002205">林</persName><persName key="A001204">遠</persName>之高風，有<persName key="A001598">肇</persName><persName key="A002842">融</persName>之識量。聲<lb
ed="T" n="0813a10"/>譽聞徹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1004"/>，勅召充<placeName key="PL000000042410">大慈恩寺</placeName>翻經大德，次補<placeName key="PL000000042216">西<lb
ed="T" n="0813a11"/>明寺</placeName>都維那，後授<placeName key="PL000000042324">太原寺</placeName>主，皆降綸旨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1226"/>，令<lb
ed="T" n="0813a12"/>維寺任。<persName key="A002146">天皇</persName>之代，以其博考<name>儒</name><name>釋</name>，雅著篇<lb
ed="T" n="0813a13"/>章，妙辯雲飛，益思泉湧，加以直詞正色，不<lb
ed="T" n="0813a14"/>憚威嚴，赴火蹈湯，無所屈撓<ptr target="#n2168"/>。頻召入內，<lb
ed="T" n="0813a15"/>與黃冠對論。皆<anchor xml:id="beg0813sgsz3"/>愜<anchor xml:id="end0813sgsz3"/><ref type="person" target="#A002146">帝</ref>旨，事在別傳<ptr target="#n2167"/>。<persName key="A001194">立</persName>以<persName key="A000294">玄<lb
ed="T" n="0813a16"/>奘<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>求經<placeName key="PL000000048207">印度</placeName>，若無紀述，季代罕聞，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0813a17"/>撰《慈恩三藏行傳》<ptr target="#n2169"/>，未成而卒。後<placeName key="PL000000042305">廣福寺</placeName>沙門<lb
ed="T" n="0813a18"/><persName key="A000827">彥悰</persName>續而成之，總十卷。故初題云「沙門<persName key="A001194">惠立</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0813a19"/>本，<persName key="A000827">釋彥悰</persName>箋」是也<ptr target="#n2170"/>。<persName key="A001194">立</persName>削藁云畢，慮遺諸美，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0813a20"/>藏諸地府，世莫得聞。爾後臨終，令門侍掘<lb
ed="T" n="0813a21"/>以啟之，將出，乃即終焉。初<persName key="A001194">立</persName>見尚醫奉御<lb
ed="T" n="0813a22"/><persName key="A011748">呂才</persName>妄造《釋因明圖注》三卷<ptr target="#n2172"/>，非斥諸師正義。<lb
ed="T" n="0813a23"/><persName key="A001194">立</persName>致書責之，其警句有云：「奉御於俗事少<lb
ed="T" n="0813a24"/>閑，遂謂真宗可了，何異乎鼷鼠見釜竈之<lb
ed="T" n="0813a25"/>堪陟，乃言<placeName key="PL000000047443">崑丘</placeName>之非難<ptr target="#n489"/>；蛛蝥覩棘林之易<lb
ed="T" n="0813a26"/>羅，亦謂<placeName key="PL000000055488">扶桑</placeName>之可<anchor xml:id="beg0813003"/>網<anchor xml:id="end0813003"/>。不量涯分<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1007"/>，何殊此<lb
ed="T" n="0813a27"/>焉？」<persName key="A011748">才</persName>由茲而寢。太常博士<persName key="A011749">柳宣</persName>聞其事息，<lb
ed="T" n="0813a28"/>乃歸信，以書〈檄翻經僧眾〉<ptr target="#n2171"/>，云「<ref type="person" target="#A001194">其</ref>外禦其侮，<lb
ed="T" n="0813a29"/><name>釋</name>門之<persName key="A002891">季路</persName>也。」</p>
